%N A393107 Primes in the Flavius Josephus's Sieve sequence (A000960).
%H A393107 Robert Israel, <a href="/A393107/b393107.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..1500</a>
%e A393107 13 is a term, it is the 6th term of A000040 (2, 3, 5, 7, 11, 13) and also the 4th term of A000960 (1, 3, 7, 13).
%p A393107 S:= [$1..10^5]: nS:= 10^5:
%p A393107 for k from 2 while k <= nS do
%p A393107   R:= [seq(i*k,i=1..floor(nS/k))];
%p A393107   S:= subsop(seq(r=NULL,r=R),S);
%p A393107   nS:= nS-floor(nS/k);
%p A393107 od:
%p A393107 select(isprime,S); # _Robert Israel_, Mar 01 2026
%Y A393107 Intersection of A000960 and A000040.
